name: Split System Change-Out (2–3 Ton)
description: Professional removal and replacement of existing split system. Includes standard installation materials, refrigerant recovery, reconnect to existing electrical and drain, full system startup and testing, manufacturer warranty registration, and homeowner walkthrough. Does not include electrical upgrades, ductwork modifications, line set replacement, access difficulty, or permits unless noted.
